  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bca\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb8\u0bcd \u0b8a\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc8 \u0b95\u0bb5\u0ba9\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8e\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95 \u0bb5\u0bc7\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd\u00a0 : \u0b9c\u0bc7.\u0bb5\u0bbf.\u0baa\u0bbf,",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "People should not ignore police curfew: JVP",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "The People's Liberation Front said that the government has no right to stifle people's protests by implementing different laws.",
        "The government has no right to suppress people's protests by implementing different laws. The Inspector General of Police does not have the authority to implement curfew without any basic reason. So people don't need to pay attention to this, he said."
      ],
